column2: b'Crayon Shin-chan Movie 07: Bakuhatsu! Onsen Wakuwaku Daikessen'

b'The Nohara family and "Onsen G-Men", the secret government agency maintaining all the hot springs in Japan, fight against "Yuzame", a bath-hating terrorist organization plotting to wipe out all the hot springs in Japan.\n\n(Source: Manabu Tsuribe)'
